methods.name: GetChainSettingsFromRetargetAsset
methods.doc: Returns the chain settings associated with a given target chain in an IK Retargeter Asset using the given profile name (optional)

methods.name: GetChainSettingsFromRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Returns the chain settings associated with a given target chain in the supplied Retarget Profile.

methods.name: GetChainUsingGoalFromRetargetAsset
methods.doc: Returns the chain settings associated with a given Goal in an IK Retargeter Asset using the given profile name (optional)

methods.name: GetGlobalSettingsFromRetargetAsset
methods.doc: Returns the global settings in an IK Retargeter Asset using the given profile name (optional)

methods.name: GetGlobalSettingsFromRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Returns the global settings in the supplied Retarget Profile.

methods.name: GetRootSettingsFromRetargetAsset
methods.doc: Returns the root settings in an IK Retargeter Asset using the given profile name (optional)

methods.name: GetRootSettingsFromRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Returns the root settings in the supplied Retarget Profile.

methods.name: SetChainFKSettingsInRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Set the chain FK settings in a retarget profile (will set bApplyChainSettings to true).

methods.name: SetChainIKSettingsInRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Set the chain IK settings in a retarget profile (will set bApplyChainSettings to true).

methods.name: SetChainSettingsInRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Set the chain settings in a retarget profile (will set bApplyChainSettings to true).

methods.name: SetChainSpeedPlantSettingsInRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Set the chain Speed Plant settings in a retarget profile (will set bApplyChainSettings to true).

methods.name: SetGlobalSettingsInRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Set the global settings in a retarget profile (will set bApplyGlobalSettings to true).

methods.name: SetRootSettingsInRetargetProfile
methods.doc: Set the root settings in a retarget profile (will set bApplyRootSettings to true).
